title: Navy Pier Holiday Cards
description:
The artist of this design, Natalia Virafuentes, says "I love to paint. I hope that my paintings encourage more people to create art. One day, I hope to be a great tattoo artist and painter". These unique holiday cards were created by a student employed in the Marwen Foundation career development programs. Marwen is an after-school arts organization that provides high-quality visual arts, college planning, and career development programs--all free of charge--to Chicago's under-served young people.

  • Dimensions: Cards 5 x 7 in.
  • Materials: Box set of 12 cards w/envelopes
  • Inside Message: Happy Holidays!
